quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  28,51,"Gom…óii Men hewtinii …ďe Konngol ngol, belajo'o, …ďe waajitora"
  28,52,"∆Āen …ďe Men rokki Deftere [Tawreeta] nden, ko adii [Alqur'aana] ndee, ko …ďe gom…óim…ďe nde"
  28,53,"Si nde janngaama e dow ma…ď…ďe, …ďe wi'a: \"Men gom…óinii nde. Ko nde goonga immorde ka Joomi amen. Pellet men woniino jebbilii…ďe, ado mayre"
  28,54,"∆Āen …óon, …ďe jonniroyte njo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe ndin, laabi …ói…ói, sabu ko …ďe mu√Īinoo kon, hi…ďe du√Īiraynoo mo∆ī∆īere nden, bone on, e huunde nde Men arsiki …ďe nden, hi…ďe nafqa"
  28,55,"Si …ďe nanii meerente, …ďe …óuurnoo e …óum, …ďe wi'a: \"Ko menen golle amen woodani, ko onon kadi golle mon woodani. Kisal wonii e mo'on. Men …óa…ď…ďataa wonndugol e majju…ďe …ďen"
  28,56,"Pellet, an (Nulaa…óo), a fewnataa mo yi…óu…óaa; kono Alla no fewna on Mo O muuyi. Ko Kanko …ďuri anndude feewu…ďe …ďen"
  28,57,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Si men jokkidii peewal ngal e maa, men biftete ka leydi amen\". E Men ho…óiniraali …ďe e nokku horminaa…óo, hoolnii…óo, mo dim…óe noone kaka addetee e mun, arsike immorde ka Amen? Si ko woni, ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe anndaa"
  28,58,"∆äuu…óii ko Men hakli, e yim…ďe ca'e, bewrunoo…ďe nguuree mun, e hino non galleeji ma…ď…ďe …óin, ho…óiraaka …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe, si wanaa see…óa. Men laatii wonnde ronoo…ďe …ďen"
  28,59,"Joomi maa siforaali wonde halkoowo yim…ďe ca'e, haa O immina e lenyol ma…ď…ďe…óen, Nulaa…óo, ko janngana …ďe Aayeeje Amen …óen. Men siforaali kadi halkugol yim…ďe ca'e, si wanaa hara yim…ďe majje ko too√Īu…ďe"
